OL,3,CDisgraced surgeon refuses to attend
OL,4,Cfirst of 62 inquests into deaths of
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FDisgraced surgeon Ian Paterson has
OL,8,Frefused to attend the first of more
OL,9,Fthan 60 inquests touching on the
OL,10,Fdeaths of his former patients because
OL,11,Fhe believes the coroner's
OL,12,Finvestigation is "biased", the court
OL,13,Fhas been told.
