OL,3,CDisgraced surgeon refuses to attend
OL,4,Cfirst of 62 inquests into deaths of
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FThe breast surgeon, who is serving a
OL,8,F20-year prison sentence after being
OL,9,Fconvicted of multiple counts of
OL,10,Fwounding in 2017, was ordered by
OL,11,Fcoroner Richard Foster to appear
OL,12,Fremotely at Birmingham and Solihull
OL,13,FCoroner's Court on Tuesday to give
OL,14,Fevidence at the inquest of Chloe
OL,15,FNikitas, who died at the age of 43 in
OL,16,FApril 2008.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/9
