OL,3,CDisgraced surgeon refuses to attend
OL,4,Cfirst of 62 inquests into deaths of
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FPaterson performed a "cleavage-sparing
OL,8,Fmastectomy" on Ms Nikitas, from
OL,9,FTamworth, leaving behind breast
OL,10,Ftissue, after she was diagnosed with
OL,11,Fgrade two ductal carcinoma in 2002,
OL,12,Fbut her cancer returned in 2005 and
OL,13,Fwas terminal.
OL,15,FMr Foster issued a ruling on Monday
OL,16,Fsaying he could "find no reason" why
OL,17,FPaterson could not attend the inquest
OL,18,Fand give evidence remotely from prison
OL,19,Fand said it was "disappointing" to the
OL,20,Ffamilies of the victims that he had
OL,21,Fdecided not to appear.
