OL,4,Cfirst of 62 inquests into deaths of
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FPaterson, 66, had been accused of
OL,8,Fattempting to delay the hearings after
OL,9,Flodging an application to have his
OL,10,Fwitness summons revoked the day before
OL,11,Fthe first inquest was due to start on
OL,12,FOctober 10, citing health concerns, a
OL,13,Flack of legal representation and
OL,14,F"inadequate facilities to prepare".
OL,16,FDespite the ruling by Mr Foster, who
OL,17,Fsaid he needed to hear Paterson's
OL,18,Fevidence at all 62 inquests, the
OL,19,Fjailed surgeon still refused to attend
OL,20,FMs Nikitas's hearing on Tuesday
OL,21,Fafternoon.
