OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FA prison supervisor told the inquest
OL,8,Fhe had had a 20-minute conversation
OL,9,Fwith Paterson on Tuesday morning, in
OL,10,Fwhich the prisoner said he felt the
OL,11,F"coroner isn't investigating fairly"
OL,12,Fand that the proceedings are "biased".
OL,14,FHe said: "(Paterson) said he is not
OL,15,Fbeing disrespectful, but feels he is
OL,16,Fnot being listened to."
