OL,3,CDisgraced surgeon refuses to attend
OL,4,Cfirst of 62 inquests into deaths of
OL,5,Cpatients
OL,7,FJonathan Jones KC, counsel to the
OL,8,Finquests, said Mr Foster had a number
OL,9,Fof powers available to him, including
OL,10,Fimposing a fine of up to #1,000 on
OL,11,FPaterson, a referral for possible
OL,12,Fprosecution for not appearing or a
OL,13,Freferral to the Attorney General for
OL,14,Fcontempt of court.
OL,16,FMr Foster said he would reserve his
OL,17,Fjudgment in the hopes that Paterson
OL,18,Fwould change his mind and attend
OL,19,Ffuture inquests.
