OL,7,FHe said: "I am disappointed that he
OL,8,Fhas not complied with the Schedule 5
OL,9,Fnotice to attend today.
OL,11,F"It is a disappointment to me, but
OL,12,Fmore importantly to the bereaved
OL,13,Ffamilies who have questions that need
OL,14,Fanswering.
OL,16,F"I said he should attend if only out
OL,17,Fof respect for the families of the 62
OL,18,Fvictims.
