OL,7,F"I had given permission to appear
OL,8,Fremotely at his request and the prison
OL,9,Fare being exceptionally co-operative
OL,10,Fto assist me and that is an ongoing
OL,11,Fobligation in each of the inquests.
OL,13,F"I hope he will review and reconsider
OL,14,Fhis position.
OL,16,F"I'm satisfied I can continue without
OL,17,Fhis attendance.
