OL,7,F"The appropriate course of action is
OL,8,Fto reserve my position in the hope for
OL,9,Fhim to attend future inquests and I
OL,10,Fwill return to this issue in due
OL,11,Fcourse.
OL,13,F"I will proceed without his
OL,14,Fparticipation."
OL,16,FThe inquest continues.
